                  <td align="left" valign="top" class="bodytext"> <p class="bodytext style2 style3">For the latest information regarding funding for 2006/07 
                      please contact the <a href="mailto:studentfinance@tasc.ac.uk">Student 
                       Adviser</a>. If you apply to Trinity and All Saints 
                      we will aim to keep you up to date on any developments in 
                    relation to fees and finance throughout 2006.</p>
                    <p class="bodytext style1 style2"><a href="#contacts">Contacts at the College</a></p>
                    <p class="bodytext style1 style2"><a href="#websites">Useful websites</a></p>
                    <p class="bodytext style1 style2"><a href="http://www.leedstrinity.ac.uk/moneymatters">Money Matters</a> - advise on budgeting, debt, benefits, mature students, EU students, overseas students and more . . . .   </p>
