                      Student  Adviser<br>
                      Room AG09A, Tel: 0113 283 7173<br>
                      Email: <a href="mailto:studentfinance@leedstrinity.ac.uk">studentfinance@leedstrinity.ac.uk</a><br>
                      Appointments can be made  via 
                      the tick box system outside Room AG09A in the Student Support 
                      Centre. <br>
                      <strong>For students on placement, out of hours appointments 
                    can be made by contacting Student Finance directly.</strong></p>
                    <hr> <p class="bodytext"><strong>Judith Atkinson</strong><br>
                      Student Support Administrator<br>
