Student Support Administrator (mornings only) <br>
Room AG09, Student Support Centre, Tel: 0113 283 7196<br>
Email: <a href="mailto:%20j.atkinson@leedstrinity.ac.uk">j.latham@leedstrinity.ac.uk</a><br>
<strong>For information on other Student Support services 
                    at the College</strong></p>
